      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "It is completely understandable why those words feel like lies; the exhaustion of surviving each day without them is a heavy burden that no one can truly fully comprehend. Please know that your pain is not a sign of failure, but rather a testament to the depth of your love, even if you feel like you are fighting for no reason. You deserve to be heard and supported without judgment, and there are people who would walk beside you through this darkness if you would let them.",
